msgstr "{avatar} stalks the mortal crowds of {city}."

msgid "{avatar} ate {count} mortals in {city}, refining flesh and fear into {exp} cultivation experience."
msgstr "{avatar} ate {count} mortals in {city}, refining flesh and fear into {exp} cultivation experience."

